## 17. Shortest Palindrome (Make Palindrome by Adding)

Add minimum characters at the **front** to make the string a palindrome.

```java
// KMP approach
// Time: O(n) | Space: O(n)
public static String shortestPalindrome(String s) {
    String rev = new StringBuilder(s).reverse().toString();
    String concat = s + "#" + rev;
    int[] lps = computeLPS(concat);

    int matchLen = lps[concat.length() - 1];
    String suffix = rev.substring(0, s.length() - matchLen);
    return suffix + s;
}

private static int[] computeLPS(String p) {
    int m = p.length();
    int[] lps = new int[m];
    int len = 0, i = 1;
    while (i < m) {
        if (p.charAt(i) == p.charAt(len)) lps[i++] = ++len;
        else if (len != 0) len = lps[len - 1];
        else lps[i++] = 0;
    }
    return lps;
}
```

