## 🔁 DP Template for String Problems

```java
// General 2D DP template
int m = s1.length(), n = s2.length();
int[][] dp = new int[m + 1][n + 1];

// Base case: empty string
for (int i = 0; i <= m; i++) dp[i][0] = /* base value */;
for (int j = 0; j <= n; j++) dp[0][j] = /* base value */;

// Fill DP table
for (int i = 1; i <= m; i++) {
    for (int j = 1; j <= n; j++) {
        if (s1.charAt(i-1) == s2.charAt(j-1)) {
            dp[i][j] = /* match case */;
        } else {
            dp[i][j] = /* mismatch case: combine subproblems */;
        }
    }
}
return dp[m][n];
