## 🔍 Key Decision Guide

```
String problem type?
├── Pattern search in text?
│   ├── Single pattern, performance critical → KMP / Z Algorithm
│   ├── Multiple patterns → Rabin-Karp / Aho-Corasick
│   └── Simple → s.contains() or s.indexOf()
│
├── Two string comparison?
│   ├── Contiguous common → Longest Common Substring (DP)
│   ├── Non-contiguous common → LCS (DP)
│   ├── Transform s1 to s2 → Edit Distance (DP)
│   └── Matching with wildcards → Wildcard DP
│
├── Palindrome problem?
│   ├── Check single → Two Pointer O(n)
│   ├── Longest palindrome substring → Expand Center O(n²)
│   ├── Longest palindrome subsequence → DP O(n²)
│   └── Min cuts → Palindrome Partitioning DP
│
└── Substring/window problems?
    ├── Fixed window → Sliding Window + frequency array
    └── Variable window → Two pointer + HashMap
```

